{
  "texts": [
    "The challenging part of the DL-based approaches applied on image synthesis is the paucity of datasets available for training and testing the different methods.",
    "Several studies are conducted with a minimum of 10 patients.",
    "Studies have also suggested that a higher number of images in the dataset can improve the performance of Deep Learning (DL) models.",
    "To improve model performance, diversity of training datasets is required.",
    "The images used for most of the studies were taken from adult patients."
  ]
}